author: IGN
description:
Watch a Warhammer expert react to your 40K questions! How would you explain Warhammer lore to someone who knows almost nothing about it? Well, we got Arbitor Ian, a Warhammer 40,000 master, to answer a mix of novice, adept, and expert-level questions. Ever wanted to know the difference between a Space Marine and the Deathwatch? Do the Chaos Gods have actual bodies? Has the Emperor of Mankind ever been spoken to after sitting on the Golden Throne? All this and more from this Warhammer 40K expert.

Arbitor Ian is a Warhammer content creator with a focus on introducing 40K lore to newcomers and veterans alike. You can watch his videos here: https://www.youtube.com/@UCHOFy9rDa1Zsvb39hYBBVpA
title: Warhammer 40K Expert Answers Your Novice, Adept, and Expert Questions
